  74,5,"Sanamuuji …óin, wo…ó…óito-…óaa"
  74,6,Wata a okkir fii he…ďugol ko …ďuri …óum
  74,7,"Ko fii Joomi maa, mu√Ī√Īortaa"
  74,8,Si wuttaama ka allaandu
  74,9,"haray nden √Īalnde woni, √Īalaande sattunde"
  74,10,"e hoore heefer…ďe …ďen, nde wanaa newiinde"
  74,11,Accidam e mo Mi tagi on ka√Īun tun
  74,12,Mi wa…óani mo jawdi …óuu…óundi
  74,13,e …ďi…ó…ďe wonndu…ďe e makko
  74,14,Mi ya√Ī√Īani mo ya√Ī√Īudee
  74,15,refti himo tam∆īinoo nde mi …ďeydata
  74,16,∆äum wa…óataa ! Tawde o laatino sanndal…óii…óo e Aayeeje Amen …óen
  74,17,Aray Mi fawa mo lette sattu…óe
  74,18,"Kanko on, o miijiti o e…ď…ďindii"
  74,19,O hu…óaama hono no o hoddiri
  74,20,Refti o hu…óa hono o hoddiri
  74,21,Refti o ndaari
  74,22,Refti √Īir…ďanii o …ďeydi √Īir…ďinaade
  74,23,Refti o runtii hombo mawnikini
  74,24,"…ďe wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ďanngu ngu"
  74,25,Mbo wonah si wonah konngol aade
  74,26,Ma Mi naatnu mbo yiite saqara
  74,27,Hol ko anndin ma ko woni Saqara
  74,28,Nge heddatah nge accatah
  74,29,Sumoowe geece
  74,30,Ina e dow mannge sappa e jeenay
  74,31,"Men wa…óaali aynoo…ďe yim…ďe Yiite ngen, si wanaa Malaa'ika. Men wa…óiraali limoore ma…ď…ďe si wanaa jarraborgol yeddu…ďe …ďen, e fii yo henan okkaa…ďe Defte …ďen, e fii no gom…óim…ďe …ďen …ďeydora gom…óinal, e fii wata okkaa…ďe Defte …ďen e gom…óim…ďe …ďen sikkito; e fii yo …ďen …ďe √Īawu woni e …ďer…óe mun e heefer…ďe …ďen wi'u: \"Hara ko hon…óum Allah faandorii e ngal misal?\" Ko wano non Allah majjinirta mo O muuyani, himo fewna kadi mo O muuyani. Hay gooto anndaa yeru koneeli Joomi maa …óin, si wanaa Kanko. Ngen [Yiite] wonaali, si wanaa waaju wonannde ne…ó…óanke"
  74,32,Kono yo henane! Mi woondirii lewru ndun
  74,33,O woondiri jemma si mbo runtii ma
  74,34,E subaka si mbo fooyni
  74,35,Ko mbo gootel e maw…ói
  74,36,Ko nge jertinirde wonannde ne…ó…óanke
  74,37,"Wonannde on yi…óu…óo e mo'on, nde o yaccotoo maa nennoo"
  74,38,Wonkii kala ko faggii kon nanngirte
  74,39,Si wanaa yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen
  74,40,"hi…ďe e nder gese, hi…ďe lamndondira"
  74,41,fii bom…ďe …ďen
  74,42,ko ho…óum naadi on Saqara
  74,43,"∆Āen wi'a: \"Men jeyanooka e juuloo…ďe …ďen"
  74,44,men jeyanooka kadi e √Īamminoo…ďe miskim…ďe …ďen
  74,45,Hari men jumpidayno kadi e jumpoo…ďe …ďen
  74,46,Hari kadi men fennayno fii √Īalaande njo…ďdi nden
  74,47,"Haa [maayde] yananaande nden arani men"
  74,48,Nafataa…ďe tefoore tefoo…ďe
  74,49,Hol ko wa…ói …ďe sirku…ďe na …óuurno Quraana
  74,50,Ho…ďe mba*i e bam…ói laawatoo…ói na ndoga
  74,51,Dok…ói mbaroodi
  74,52,Gooto e mum en fof na faaala totteede …óeri caraa…ói
  74,53,Alah woni ko…ďe kulaani laakara
  74,54,Alah …óuum ko ciftanirgol
  74,55,Ko kala faalaa…óo waactaroo mbo o waaccaroo mbo
  74,56,"…ďe mbaactaaka si wonah Alla na haaja, ko Kanko woni kaandu…óo e huleede ko Kanko woni kaandu…óo e yaafaade"